Plot:
Five young students have just enrolled in Thailand's most prestigious St.George's School. On a display of past awards and achievements of old students, the new comers disover that in 1952, 6 old boys had mysteriously committed suicide, one of them was a handsome prince. The boys firmly believe that there must be something hebind all this, and form a committee to investigate. To seek the truth, they even resort to supernatural powers to get in touch with the dead prince.
